attributeList.attribute: Reversibly binds Fe-S clusters and appears to play a role in Fe-S cluster assembly and trafficking. May also participate in the maturation of [4Fe-4S]2+ cluster-containing proteins in a glutathione-independent manner, possibly as a carrier protein to mediate the transfer of preassembled [4Fe-4S]2+ cluster to target proteins. Active in the mitchondria.
